# Identifying Source Host

Command concept:

```
cut -f1 dns_entropy.log | sort | uniq
```

Purpose:

```
identify originating hosts
```

Result:

```
all traffic from 172.31.64.10
```

Meaning:

```
critical server exfiltrating data
```

